Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.66,0:00:02.86,Kingdom-Thought,,0,0,0,,This is the air of a battlefield, huh?  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.70,0:00:02.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂(てん)）戦う前から これかよ…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,のまれるものか！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.67,0:00:05.46,Kingdom-Thought,,0,0,0,,Like hell I'm going to let this swallow me!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.76,0:00:11.43,Kingdom-Thought,Bing,0,0,0,,The Feixin Unit headquarters got behind us before I had laid out my encircling net {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.80,0:00:11.34,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷鬼(ひょうき)）俺が包囲網を敷く前に\N飛信(ひしん)隊本陣は裏へ抜けていた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.43,0:00:14.59,Kingdom-Thought,Bing,0,0,0,,and they joined up with their scattered soldiers. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.51,0:00:14.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして\N散開していた兵とも合流していた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.81,0:00:18.21,Kingdom-Thought,Bing,0,0,0,,This rapid reorganization... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.84,0:00:18.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この迅速な立て直し…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.65,0:00:22.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,明らかに 何者かが\N参謀として隊に加入している
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.74,0:00:22.49,Kingdom-Thought,Bing,0,0,0,,It is clear that someone has joined their unit as a staff officer! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.47,0:00:27.96,Kingdom-Thought,Bing,0,0,0,,I will measure what level of strategist it is with this move! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:23.52,0:00:27.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どの程度の軍師か\Nこの一手で測らせてもらう
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.37,0:00:31.28,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Here they come!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.43,0:00:32.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田孝(でんこう)）来た 敵先鋒隊(せんぽうたい)！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.28,0:00:32.50,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The enemy vanguard!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.13,0:00:36.66,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,They've suddenly moved 1,000 of their 4,000 soldiers. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.30,0:00:36.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,全軍4,000のうちの1,000を\Nいきなり動かしてきた
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.23,0:00:40.33,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,And this is an elite unit! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.30,0:00:40.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかも あれは精鋭部隊か！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.04,0:00:43.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦を急いでいるということじゃない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.09,0:00:43.62,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,They're not trying to hurry the battle. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.87,0:00:46.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田孝）河了貂(かりょうてん)！\N迎撃しないと 敵が どんどん…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.89,0:00:47.15,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,He Liao Diao, unless we meet them, the enemy will keep getting closer...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.04,0:00:48.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいんだ！\N（田孝）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.15,0:00:48.27,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,It's all right!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.01,0:00:52.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）向こうからは見えていない
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.07,0:00:52.20,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,They can't see from over there,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.54,0:00:58.34,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,but there are a lot of forked paths in the State of Wei's way!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.55,0:00:58.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏国(ぎこく)軍の行く手には\Nいくつもの岐路があることを！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.03,0:01:05.04,Kingdom - Episode Title,Title,0,0,0,,{\fs80\be0\c&H000000&\pos(600,130)}Outwit
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.91,0:01:21.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,オオッ！ 敵が分散したぞ\N（貂）よし！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.95,0:01:20.70,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,Oh, the enemy has split up!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.98,0:01:21.89,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:27.66,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Not only are their numbers divided, but the path gets even narrower so that their impact point is smaller.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.74,0:01:27.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,兵力が分散したうえに\Nその先は狭いから 衝突面が小さい
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.49,0:01:32.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）だから―
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.52,0:01:32.51,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,So...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.51,0:01:37.02,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,500 will be more than enough to defeat their force of 1,000!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.62,0:01:36.89,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,1,000に対し500の兵力で\N十分 打ち勝つことができるんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.32,0:01:54.82,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,First, using a heavyweight unit we dam up one road tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.44,0:01:54.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まずは重量級の部隊で\Nひとつの道をガッチリ せき止める
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.88,0:01:57.38,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（槍兵(やりへい)たち）トリャー！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.75,0:02:02.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）そこから更に 力ずくで前進\N敵を分岐点まで押し戻す
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.77,0:02:00.65,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,After that, we'll push forward with all our might
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.65,0:02:03.01,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,and bring the enemy back to the fork.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.58,0:02:08.35,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,If we do that, the entrances to individual smaller paths will be closed off.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.62,0:02:08.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうすれば それぞれの小道は\N入り口に蓋をされた状態になる
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.79,0:02:12.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵Ａ）う… 後ろで異変が！\N（道清(どうせい)）なに？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.81,0:02:12.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,There's something strange going on behind us!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.08,0:02:12.81,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.03,0:02:15.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）後方に敵が！\N（魏兵）バカな！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.04,0:02:15.27,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Enemies from behind?! How?!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:20.82,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,With their path of retreat suddenly cut off, the enemy units are sure to fall into confusion.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.93,0:02:20.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,突然 退路を断たれた敵の各隊は\N必ず混乱に陥る
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.94,0:02:22.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竜有(りゅうゆう)たち）ヤーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.94,0:02:24.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平(びへい)たち）ウオーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.60,0:02:28.20,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,And we'll use that opportunity to mow them down!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.67,0:02:28.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）その機に乗じて\N一気に たたくんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.44,0:02:29.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.58,0:02:33.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）ハハッ… 弱(よえ)え！\N弱えッスよ こいつら！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:31.29,0:02:33.72,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,Man, these guys are freakin' weak!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.72,0:02:36.17,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,They're panicking because they don't have any idea what's going on!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.78,0:02:36.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竜有）状況がつかめず\N混乱してるからだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.60,0:02:41.97,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,These guys... they're like how we were just a little while ago!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.15,0:02:41.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）ヤツら まるで\Nついさっきまでの俺たちみてえだ
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.59,0:02:46.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,クッ… うろたえるな！\N退路など 初めから必要ない！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.50,0:02:44.75,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Do not lose your heads!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.75,0:02:46.72,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,We never needed a path of retreat to begin with!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.00,0:02:48.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵Ａ）千人将！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.02,0:02:48.31,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Thousand-Man General!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.16,0:02:50.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（道清）\N各隊 前の敵だけに集中しろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.31,0:02:50.85,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,All units, focus only on the enemy up ahead!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.42,0:02:53.73,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The enemies numbers are nothing significant!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.50,0:02:53.60,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵は 大した兵力ではない！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.53,0:02:57.70,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,First, form files!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.60,0:02:58.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（道清）まずは隊列を整えろ！\N（魏兵たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.91,0:03:01.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田孝）\Nクッ… マズイ！ 早くも立て直しを
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.64,0:03:02.15,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,Oh no! They're regrouping already!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.08,0:03:04.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）\Nいや 隊長の居場所が分かった
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.15,0:03:04.85,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,No, now we know where the captain is!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.88,0:03:08.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そいつを討てば\Nその隊は終わりだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:08.07,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,If you take him down, they're finished!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.02,0:03:11.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田有(でんゆう)）ンンッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:13.94,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Lord Dao Qing!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.65,0:03:16.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵たち）道清さま！\N（飛信隊兵たち）田有百人将！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.14,0:03:16.95,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Tian You Hundred-Man General!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.95,0:03:20.92,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,If I clash with you head on, you're not a match for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.96,0:03:20.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まともに かち合えりゃ\Nお前らなんて 相手じゃねえんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.79,0:03:27.22,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,E-Emergency Report!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.80,0:03:29.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（伝令）きゅ… 急報！\N道清千人将 討ち死に！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.77,0:03:29.82,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Thousand-Man General Dao Qing has been killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.81,0:03:31.81,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,隊も ほぼ壊滅しました！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.82,0:03:31.92,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,His unit is now almost wiped out as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.91,0:03:35.04,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）な… なんだと！\N（魏兵）こんな短時間で…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.93,0:03:33.42,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.42,0:03:35.23,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,In such a short amount of time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.84,0:03:37.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（間永(かんえい)）氷鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.85,0:03:37.15,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Bing Gui.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.75,0:03:39.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷鬼）甘く見過ぎたか…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:37.76,0:03:39.73,Kingdom-Thought,Bing,0,0,0,,I suppose I underestimated them. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.42,0:03:45.68,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,Entire vanguard, charge!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.55,0:03:46.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前衛全体 突撃だ！\N（魏兵たち）はっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.68,0:03:46.36,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.22,0:03:50.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,か… 河了貂 敵が！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.28,0:03:50.74,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,H-He Liao Diao, the enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.13,0:03:53.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,広がりながら前進してきたぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.18,0:03:53.61,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,They're advancing while still spread out!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:58.10,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Bing Gui, if they enter those paths...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.83,0:03:55.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（間永）氷鬼…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.23,0:04:00.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あの道に入っていっては\N同じ目に遭うのではないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:00.42,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,won't they just meet the same fate as the others?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.42,0:04:02.32,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,No need to worry.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.57,0:04:04.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ご心配なく\N先ほどの敵の戦術は―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.32,0:04:09.22,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,The enemy's current strategy will only be effective if our army is focused on a narrow path.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.64,0:04:09.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あくまで 我が軍が隘路(あいろ)に\N集中した場合に効果を得る代物
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:13.47,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,If our units fragment and take every path
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.05,0:04:13.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,部隊を細分化して\Nあらゆる道から進ませれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.47,0:04:16.77,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,then a small number of enemies will not be able to stop them all.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.58,0:04:16.69,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,少数のヤツらに\N全ては止められませぬ
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:21.02,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,And if we make it through, then we will reach the heart of the enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.55,0:04:20.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,抜ければ\N部隊は一気に敵の心臓部へ届きます
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.06,0:04:26.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,攻略が早い…\Nやっぱり手ごわいぞ この敵
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.09,0:04:23.95,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,They're attacking quickly! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.95,0:04:26.24,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,This really is a strong enemy! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.13,0:04:30.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田孝）ああっ！\N無人の道に どんどん敵が！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.14,0:04:30.28,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,Enemies are entering un-manned paths one after another!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.76,0:04:32.01,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,He Liao Diao!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.83,0:04:31.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,河了貂！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.07,0:04:35.67,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）隘路の戦は終わりだ\N（田孝）も… もう？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.09,0:04:34.77,Kingdom-Main,DIao,0,0,0,,The narrow path battles are over!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.77,0:04:35.77,Kingdom-Main,Xioa,0,0,0,,A-Already?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.49,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Have the spread out units gather towards Xin on the right!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.77,0:04:38.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）張ってる各隊を\N右の信(しん)のもとに集めろ！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.49,0:04:40.92,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,The right?! Not on the defense of us, the headquarters?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.57,0:04:40.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田孝）\N右に？ ここの守備じゃないのか？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.24,0:04:44.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここの守りに\N力を割く余裕なんてない！
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.27,0:04:44.19,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,We can't afford to divide our power in order to protect us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.48,0:04:47.50,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I intended to leave this place exposed from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.61,0:04:46.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初めから\Nここは野ざらしにするつもりだった
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.08,0:04:48.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ええっ？ そ… そんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.50,0:04:48.63,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.74,0:04:52.18,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,By exposing us, I'll draw the enemy this way. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.82,0:04:52.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あえて さらして 敵を引き付ける
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.61,0:04:58.18,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,With the Feixin Unit being injured as well as short on numbers, it can't be a drawn out fight. {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.69,0:04:56.52,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,数が少ないうえに\N既に傷ついてる飛信隊が勝つには
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,長期戦ではなく―
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.63,0:05:00.69,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,We can only win with an incredibly short battle!  {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.69,0:05:00.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,極端な短期戦！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.04,0:05:03.31,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Let's go, you bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.06,0:05:04.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いくぞ てめえらー！\N（兵士たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.56,0:05:10.57,Kingdom-Thought,Xin,0,0,0,,Before our headquarters falls, you've got to take out the enemy headquarters... and win! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.70,0:05:10.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっちの本陣が落ちる前に\N敵本陣を落として 勝つ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.96,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Enemies incoming from the left!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.31,0:05:17.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）左方より\N敵が こっちに向かってきます！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.08,0:05:20.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（間永）う～ん… ここ狙いか
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.28,0:05:21.17,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Targeting the headquarters, are they?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.17,0:05:22.54,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,Fools.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.18,0:05:22.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,バカが…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.01,0:05:25.14,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.02,0:05:25.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田孝）いけ！ いけー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.32,0:05:28.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙毅(もうき)）河了貂…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.37,0:05:28.63,Kingdom-Flashback,Yi,0,0,0,,He Liao Diao.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.78,0:05:34.85,Kingdom-Flashback,Yi,0,0,0,,There are primarily two ways of breaking through an enemy headquarters with a massive defense.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.83,0:05:34.76,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙毅）分厚く守る敵本陣を\N破る手段は 主に２つある
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.49,0:05:38.53,Kingdom-Flashback,Yi,0,0,0,,But for the most part, the method used in actual battle
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.60,0:05:38.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙毅）しかし\N実戦で使われる手段のほとんどは
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.53,0:05:41.90,Kingdom-Flashback,Yi,0,0,0,,is relying on power and forcing one's way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.63,0:05:41.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,結局のところ\N武の力に頼った強行突破だ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.63,0:05:46.04,Kingdom-Flashback,Yi,0,0,0,,Of course, large sacrifices accompany using that strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.74,0:05:45.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もちろん\Nその手は大きな犠牲を伴う
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.98,0:05:52.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）ドリャー！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.61,0:05:56.58,Kingdom-Flashback,Yi,0,0,0,,But it is because of that sacrifice that it brings about such a tremendous result.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:56.62,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙毅）でも だからこそ\N絶大な効果を生みだすんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.32,0:06:00.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（竜有）隊長に続け！\N（兵士たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.34,0:05:59.19,Kingdom-Main,Long,0,0,0,,Follow the captain!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.61,0:06:02.54,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The left is now in combat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.72,0:06:03.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）左 戦闘に入りました！\N押し込まれています！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.54,0:06:03.96,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,They're being pushed back!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.33,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,Do not panic!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.96,0:06:05.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷鬼）うろたえるな！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.57,0:06:07.68,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,Send reinforcements to thicken the defense!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.66,0:06:08.66,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,増援を送り 厚みを作れ！\N（魏兵）ははっ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.68,0:06:08.76,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.96,0:06:13.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,フッ… なんだ\N結局 最後は策なく いつもの力業か
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.79,0:06:13.87,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Well now. It looks like in the end, they went with their usual not-thought-out brute force attack, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.55,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Seems they didn't have much of a strategist after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.87,0:06:16.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ハハッ…\N大した軍師ではなかったな
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.96,0:06:20.64,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,No, forcing their way through is a fine strategy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.97,0:06:20.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いえ 強行突破は立派な策です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.31,0:06:24.18,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実戦では 敵も知恵を絞るゆえ―
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.38,0:06:24.29,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,Because in actual battles the enemy always thinks very carefully as well,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.28,0:06:28.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実際のところ 奇策だけで\N勝利することは ほぼ ありません
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.29,0:06:28.40,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,there are few battles that can be won on clever schemes alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:33.40,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,And one strategy you can be almost sure to find in the endgame is forcing one's way through.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.98,0:06:33.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最終的な一手は\N必ずといっていいほど強行突破です
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.32,0:06:38.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷鬼）要は\Nその一手を どこで使うかですが…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.37,0:06:38.41,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,But as for how that fundamental move is being used,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.78,0:06:41.93,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,with the enemy strategist having targeted it for the moment just after we sent our attack,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.83,0:06:41.83,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こちらが\N攻めに出た直後をねらった敵軍師は
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.33,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,one could say they made the best possible choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.93,0:06:44.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最良の選択をしたと言えます
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.66,0:06:48.13,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Hey now, Bing Gui, you're praising them an awful lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.77,0:06:46.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（間永）余裕だな 氷鬼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.70,0:06:48.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やけに褒める
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.10,0:06:52.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,褒めてはおりませぬ\Nただ バカではなかったと
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.13,0:06:52.30,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,I am not praising them, I am merely stating that they are not idiots.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.06,0:06:55.62,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A four-layer defensive fomration!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:55.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵Ａ）４重防陣だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.62,0:06:57.00,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Take your positions!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:59.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵Ｂ）配置に就け！\N正面を止めて 横から そぐぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.00,0:06:59.58,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Stop the front and chip away at their sides!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.98,0:07:03.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊の力を考慮すれば―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.00,0:07:03.51,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Considering the Feixin Unit's strength,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.51,0:07:07.06,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,the previous State of Wei armies would have been defeated by this charge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.65,0:07:07.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今までの魏国軍は\Nこの突破で破れていたでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.90,0:07:10.12,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,But currently in this headquarters
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.96,0:07:13.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しかし今 本陣にいるのは\N訓練し尽くされた将軍と私の正規兵
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.12,0:07:13.44,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,are heavily-trained generals and my regular soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.88,0:07:18.20,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,And on top of that, as we have witnessed the Feixin Unit's destructive power at Shanyang,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.96,0:07:18.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その上 山陽(さんよう)で飛信隊の破壊力を\N目の当たりにした我らが―
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.55,0:07:22.70,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,we are certain not to misread how to cope with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.67,0:07:22.30,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その対応を見誤ることは\N絶対にない！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.30,0:07:24.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永(でんえい)）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.37,0:07:29.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷鬼）故に 飛信隊の勝利は\N万にひとつも ありえない
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.38,0:07:29.84,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Therefore, the Feixin Unit does not have the slimmest chance of victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.55,0:07:35.14,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Lord Xin, enemy reinforcements are flooding in!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.71,0:07:35.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕(えん)）信どの 敵の増援が一気に！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.14,0:07:37.47,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,These guys are pretty damn good at fortifying their fronts!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.15,0:07:37.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（飛信隊Ａ）こいつら\N前の固め方がハンパねえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.95,0:07:42.69,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,Th-The enemy is reacting abnormally fast!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.99,0:07:42.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田孝）\Nて… 敵の対応が異常に早い！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.69,0:07:45.10,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,Th-The captain and the others are being swallowed!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.76,0:07:45.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,た… 隊長たちが のまれていく！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.32,0:07:51.12,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,Th-The enemy's at our feet!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.33,0:07:51.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,て… 敵が足元に！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.12,0:07:52.86,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,He Liao Diao, we must seek shelter!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.17,0:07:54.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,河了貂 早く退避を！\N（貂）放っとけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.86,0:07:53.99,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Ignore them!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.44,0:07:56.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,放っとけったって…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.50,0:07:56.49,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,What, ignore them?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.13,0:07:59.66,Kingdom-Main,Xiao,0,0,0,,Stones or whatever you can get your hands on, throw something down there!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.17,0:08:01.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,石でも何でもいい 下へ投げろ！\N（兵士たち） お… おお！
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.66,0:08:01.27,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.21,0:08:04.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田孝）か… 河了貂！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.26,0:08:06.16,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,H-He Liao Diao, do we give the signal now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:07.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,合図は まだか！\N（貂）まだだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.16,0:08:07.00,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Not yet!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.93,0:08:14.38,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,Hang in there, everyone... Xin... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.98,0:08:12.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,頑張ってくれ みんな…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.46,0:08:14.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.46,0:08:15.82,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N（魏兵）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.64,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Dammit, what kinda strategy is this, brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.22,0:08:19.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪(はいろう)）クッ！ こんな作戦…\Nざけんなよ あのガキ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.92,0:08:22.77,Kingdom-Main,Chong,0,0,0,,You must still be okay if you're able to fling insults!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.03,0:08:22.46,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（崇原(すうげん)）悪態がつけるなら\Nまだ大丈夫だな！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.76,0:08:23.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うるせえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.77,0:08:23.51,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Sheddep!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.37,0:08:27.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（間永）\Nまだ つぶれぬか… しぶといな
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.40,0:08:27.67,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Have they still not fallen? How stubborn.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.67,0:08:29.27,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,Shall we settle this?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.80,0:08:29.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷鬼）もう決めましょう
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.31,0:08:32.15,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,Further reinforcements!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.34,0:08:31.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,更に増援だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.14,0:08:35.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろも囲い\N絶対に隊長 信を取り逃がすな！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.15,0:08:33.33,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,Surround them from behind as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.33,0:08:35.90,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,We must not let the captain, Xin, escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.08,0:08:40.75,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵たち）オーッ！\N（魏兵）飛信隊 信を殺せ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.16,0:08:39.53,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Kill Feixin Unit Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.13,0:08:42.72,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,Enemy reinforcements are coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.18,0:08:44.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵の増援が来る！\Nさっきより多いぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.72,0:08:44.04,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,This is even more than before!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.94,0:08:51.04,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Good.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.02,0:08:51.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よっし…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.44,0:08:53.31,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Now's the time, bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.46,0:08:56.06,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっからだ 野郎ども！\N飛信隊の底力 見せつけてやれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.31,0:08:56.76,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Let's show them the real strength of the Feixin Unit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.93,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.20,0:09:00.97,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんちきしょう！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.91,0:09:06.43,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,He Liao Diao, hurry! The enemy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.97,0:09:06.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田孝）河了貂 早く！ 敵が！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.15,0:09:13.41,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,The enemy's defenses are shifting completely towards Xin now! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.18,0:09:13.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）\N敵の守備が完全に信のほうへ偏った
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.48,0:09:16.79,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今だ！ 合図の旗！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.53,0:09:16.69,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Now! The signal flag!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.89,0:09:28.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（地響き）\N何だ？ この音は
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.69,0:09:27.95,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,What's that sound?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.84,0:09:29.96,Kingdom-Thought,Bing,0,0,0,,Behind me?! {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.93,0:09:29.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,後ろ？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.21,0:09:34.71,Kingdom-Thought,Yi,0,0,0,,And the second way of taking down an enemy headquarters, {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.27,0:09:34.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙毅）敵本陣を討つ２つ目の手段
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.37,0:09:39.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それは\N巧みな仕掛けで敵の守備に穴を開け
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:38.97,Kingdom-Thought,Yi,0,0,0,,that is to use a clever trick to open a hole in the enemy's defenses {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.87,0:09:43.47,Kingdom-Thought,Yi,0,0,0,,and launch one all-out surprise attack on them! {Flashback}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.94,0:09:43.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,一撃必殺の奇襲攻撃を加える戦術だ
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:49.48,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The Feixin Unit's Guo Bei soldiers have been sighted!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.25,0:09:50.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（烈(れつ)弟）飛信隊郭備(かくび)兵 見参！\N（兵士たち）オーッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.45,0:09:54.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（魏兵）て… 敵襲！ 敵襲です！\N（間永･氷鬼）アア…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.61,0:09:53.08,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,A-An enemy attack! Enemy attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.86,0:10:02.00,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（斬る音）\N…たく 貂のヤツ 大したもんだぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.37,0:10:02.01,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Man, that Diao really knows what she's doing!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.01,0:10:08.40,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I never guessed she'd use me as a decoy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.07,0:10:08.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか\Nこの俺を囮(おとり)に使うなんてよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.05,0:10:13.96,Kingdom - Episode Title,Sign,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,0)\fs70\be0\pos(986,90)}Xin
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:22.64,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So ya caught the enemy general, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.53,0:10:25.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,敵将を捕らえたのか！\N（烈弟）ハハハッ… やりました！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.95,0:10:25.38,Kingdom-Main,Lie,0,0,0,,We did it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.24,0:10:28.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永）\Nなんで ぶっ殺してねえんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.26,0:10:28.25,Kingdom-Main,Lie,0,0,0,,Why don't you kill us?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.24,0:10:31.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（烈弟）娘軍師に\N“できれば生け捕りにしろ”と
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.25,0:10:31.30,Kingdom-Main,Lie,0,0,0,,The strategist girl told us to take you alive if possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.27,0:10:32.48,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永）生け捕り？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.30,0:10:32.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.58,0:10:35.21,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（烈弟）\Nなんでも“平定の戦いだから”とか
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:35.23,Kingdom-Main,Lie,0,0,0,,She said because it's a suppression battle, or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.51,0:10:40.05,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まあ 本営に渡しゃ\N手柄になるから いいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.58,0:10:40.20,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,If we hand them over to the army headquarters, it'll be a real achievement, so I'm okay with it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.07,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Hey, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お… おい あれ！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.97,0:10:45.32,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,The headquarters!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.99,0:10:47.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本陣が…\N俺たちの本陣が焼け落ちてる！
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.32,0:10:47.82,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Our headquarters is being burned down!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.82,0:10:49.89,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Huh?! What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.89,0:10:49.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪）なに？ どうなってんだ？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.89,0:10:52.62,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Did our side get taken down at the same time?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.96,0:10:52.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,同時に\Nあっちも落とされたってことか？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:58.88,Kingdom-Main,Song,0,0,0,,Well, we {\i1}did{\i0} use so many soldiers to attack that there were barely any left defending for the headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.33,0:10:56.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（松左(しょうさ)）\N確かに 攻めに兵を使ったんで―
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.20,0:10:58.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本陣の守備は\Nほとんど いなかったはず…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.88,0:11:00.46,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.00,0:11:00.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… なんだって！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.12,0:11:04.61,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that brat decided to sacrifice herself?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.17,0:11:04.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,まさか\Nあのガキ 自分を犠牲にして…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.96,0:11:08.14,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Hey, don't write me off that easily!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.98,0:11:08.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こら！ 勝手に殺すな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.61,0:11:10.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）貂！\N（田永）ガキ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.65,0:11:09.62,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Diao!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.79,0:11:11.02,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.62,0:11:15.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前 あの本陣は…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.72,0:11:15.55,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What about the headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.49,0:11:19.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ああ 負けた腹いせに\Nヤツらが火でも つけたんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.55,0:11:19.41,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Looks like they lit a fire in retaliation to their defeat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.39,0:11:21.16,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あと 俺がいなかったから
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.41,0:11:21.15,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,That, and because I was gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.78,0:11:25.51,Kingdom-Main,Yuan,0,0,0,,That was quite something, escaping an enemy encirclement with so few soldiers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.89,0:11:25.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（渕）しかし よく\Nその兵の少なさで敵の包囲を…
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.51,0:11:30.29,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Well, I at least made sure to have a secure escape route from the beginning.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.53,0:11:28.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）脱出経路くらい確保しとくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.53,0:11:30.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,最初っからね
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.11,0:11:40.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（尾平）アハハッ… すっげえ！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:40.41,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.34,0:11:43.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何なんだ？ こいつは\N大したタマだぜ まったく！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.41,0:11:43.88,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Man, what's with this girl? She's really something!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:47.01,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Bing Gui?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.25,0:11:47.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うん？ 氷鬼？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.38,0:11:48.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな小娘が―
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.40,0:11:51.52,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,A little girl like this really is what allowed us to win!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.02,0:11:51.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,マジで俺たちを勝たせやがった\N（貂）ああ？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.69,0:11:54.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（沛浪）\Nこりゃ まいったぜ　なっ？ 田永
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.79,0:11:53.16,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Man, I'm beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.16,0:11:54.39,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Right, Tian Yong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.27,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Guess it looks that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:59.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永）ケッ！ たまたまだろう\N（沛浪）ハハッ… 素直じゃねえな
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.42,0:11:59.18,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,Ain't you honest?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.23,0:12:02.23,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（氷鬼）クッ… ふざけるな！\N（信･貂）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.75,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,Quit screwing around!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.30,0:12:06.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こ… こんな小娘だっただと？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.32,0:12:06.69,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,Y-You're saying it was this girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:13.95,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,I, Bing Gui, a man counted as one of the 8 best in the State of Wei, lost to this little girl?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.34,0:12:09.11,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな小娘に―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:14.01,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,魏国で８本の指に入るといわれた\Nこの氷鬼が負けただと？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.42,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,I will not accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.25,0:12:18.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は認めんぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.99,0:12:21.76,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,This surprise attack would seem absurd when looked at on a table...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.08,0:12:23.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こんな奇襲は机上の絵空事\N下策中の下策だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:23.61,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,The poorest of poor plans!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.59,0:12:28.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,たまたま 飛信隊が高い戦闘力を\N持っていたから成功したが
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.61,0:12:28.09,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,It may have succeeded merely because the Feixin Unit happened to have quite high attack power,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.39,0:12:32.60,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,but with a normal unit, the decoy would've been wiped out and the surprise attack would've also ended in failure!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.43,0:12:32.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,普通の隊なら 囮は全滅し\N奇襲も失敗に終わる
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.32,0:12:36.41,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,And I'm sure there was major damage as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.36,0:12:36.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実際 大きな被害も出たはずだ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.10,0:12:39.44,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hey,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.13,0:12:39.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）おい！
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.89,0:12:42.16,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,quit yammering, old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.00,0:12:43.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ウダウダうるせえぞ おっさん\N（氷鬼）“おっさん”？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.48,0:12:43.48,Kingdom-Main,Bing,0,0,0,,Old man?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.71,0:12:45.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）だったら こいつの策は―
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:50.45,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,If that's the case, then her plan was really awesome because it used the Feixin Unit's strengths to its fullest potential, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.64,0:12:50.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊の力を最大限に生かした\Nすげえもんだってことじゃねえか
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.90,0:12:54.09,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You lost to her in a battle of wits.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.05,0:12:54.15,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前は\N知恵比べで こいつに負けたんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.55,0:12:58.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊軍師 河了貂にな！\N（貂）ハッ…
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.59,0:12:57.34,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,The Feixun Unit strategist, He Liao Diao!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:02.57,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Make sure you get that name into your skull!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.52,0:13:02.43,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,この名前\Nよ～く頭に たたき込んどけ！
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.91,0:13:07.00,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.03,0:13:07.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）信…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.27,0:13:18.27,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Take them with us.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.31,0:13:18.27,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）連れてけ
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.98,0:13:21.82,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hell yeah! We won!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.04,0:13:21.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,しゃ！ 勝ったぞ！
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.74,0:14:27.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,よう！\N（貂）信…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.82,0:14:26.79,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.79,0:14:27.84,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.16,0:14:30.14,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What're ya doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.21,0:14:30.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,何やってんだ？ お前
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.14,0:14:33.17,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We've got a reason to be excited for the first time in a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.25,0:14:33.22,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,せっかく久々に\Nゆっくり盛り上がってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.53,0:14:34.47,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,C'mon.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.55,0:14:34.45,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,来いよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.99,0:14:36.40,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.09,0:14:36.29,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）俺は いいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.40,0:14:41.14,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I've got to come up with a plan for the terrain we're heading to next.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.42,0:14:41.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,次に行く場所の地形に合った作戦を\N考えないといけないから
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.14,0:14:43.35,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You can do that stuff tomorrow, can't ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.22,0:14:43.36,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）\N…んなもん あしたでいいだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.63,0:14:45.70,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そうはいかない！\N（信）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.69,0:14:45.46,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,No, I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.20,0:14:51.09,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,If I make just a little mistake,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.26,0:14:53.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺が少しでも間違えれば\N数十人単位で人が死んでしまうんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.09,0:14:53.99,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,dozens of people could die.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.77,0:14:56.84,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,策を練り上げておかなくちゃ
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.85,0:14:57.06,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I've got to refine my plans.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.25,0:15:02.05,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You don't need to burden yourself with the number of dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.31,0:15:01.88,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）死人の数まで お前は\Nしょい込まなくていいんだよ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.21,0:15:05.00,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Like hell I can't!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.31,0:15:07.58,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…んなわけにいくかよ！\Nしょい込むに決まってんだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.41,0:15:07.59,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Of course I need to bear that burden!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.79,0:15:12.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,戦場で指示するとき―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.85,0:15:12.94,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,When I give instructions on the battlefield
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.23,0:15:16.97,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I calculate about how many will die when I send them in!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.29,0:15:16.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は どのくらい死ぬかも\N計算に入れて 送り出してんだぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.52,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Diao...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.56,0:15:19.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,貂…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.06,0:15:23.43,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,A strategist has to have hostility.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.13,0:15:23.40,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）軍師には適性ってのがあって
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.80,0:15:26.74,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,初陣で\N一応 それは示せたと思ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.86,0:15:26.77,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,And I think I displayed that at least in that first campaign.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.90,0:15:32.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,でも 先のことを考えると\Nどうしても怖くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.00,0:15:32.32,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,But when I think about what happened, I can't help but feel scared.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:36.55,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Close to 100 of our men died in that battle.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.31,0:15:36.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,今回の戦で100人近くが死んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.61,0:15:40.68,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,“この先 何百人\N死なせていくんだろう”って…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.62,0:15:40.90,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,And now I'm thinking how many hundreds I'm going to let die after this...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.82,0:15:49.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺のこと 自分の娘に似てるって\N言ってくれたヤツも―
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.89,0:15:49.97,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,There was even a guy that said I reminded him of his daughter...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.34,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,that died in my plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.43,0:15:52.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺の作戦で死んだ
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.90,0:15:59.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,わざわざ励ましに来てくれたのに\N俺は そいつを…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.94,0:15:59.08,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,He went out of his way to cheer me up, and I...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.15,0:16:05.87,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I can't get that smile back now...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.31,0:16:05.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう取り戻せないんだ\Nあの笑顔は…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.43,0:16:13.45,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You should go home after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.48,0:16:14.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,やっぱ帰れ お前\N（貂）なっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.82,0:16:17.35,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）戦に出りゃ 誰かを殺す
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.85,0:16:17.47,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,When you go to war, you'll kill somebody.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.47,0:16:22.92,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Whether it's an ally or an enemy, you can't measure just how much blood and tears are flowing...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.52,0:16:19.49,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,味方だろうが 敵だろうが―
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.59,0:16:22.73,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,その裏で流れる血と涙は\N計り知れねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.36,0:16:28.33,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That's why we take that as part of winning and move forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.39,0:16:28.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そして 勝った者(もん)は\Nそれを全部 背負って前に行く
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.42,0:16:34.80,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,That's why the weight on our backs gets a lot heavier when we win.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.47,0:16:30.47,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だから…
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.40,0:16:34.54,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,勝つ度に\N背中は とんでもなく重くなる
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.91,0:16:43.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,そういう苦しみがあることも\N知らずに来たんなら とっとと帰れ
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.99,0:16:42.15,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,If you came here without knowing about that sorta pain,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.15,0:16:43.67,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,then you should get out of here now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.38,0:16:45.28,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）だ… 誰が帰るか！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.95,0:16:45.58,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Who said anything about leaving?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.55,0:16:47.65,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺は ただ 分かってたけど
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.58,0:16:51.61,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I'm just saying that I knew that, but it's a lot heavier than I imagined!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.75,0:16:51.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,実際 やっぱり想像以上に重いって\N話をしただけだろう
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.92,0:16:55.33,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,それに そんな軽い気持ちで\Nここに来たんじゃない！
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.94,0:16:55.49,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I didn't take coming here that lightly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.25,0:17:01.83,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Yeah, you didn't!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:01.80,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ヘヘッ… だよな！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.43,0:17:05.44,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\N（信）だから 戦場の大先輩が―
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.27,0:17:05.57,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So as someone who's far your senior as far as the battlefield goes,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.54,0:17:08.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,ここで続けてくコツを\N教えてやろうっつってんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.57,0:17:08.62,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,I'll show you the ropes for what you're gonna be up against!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.39,0:17:10.63,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,So gimme your hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.54,0:17:10.61,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手ぇ貸してみろ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.84,0:17:12.78,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,手？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.89,0:17:13.13,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.69,0:17:15.25,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,See, this is how it goes!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.71,0:17:14.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）おら！ こうすんだ！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.25,0:17:16.64,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Hey, Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.28,0:17:18.31,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）\Nお… おい 信！ ちょ… 痛い！
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.64,0:17:18.26,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.67,0:17:20.21,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Never mind, c'mon!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.68,0:17:21.32,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,いいから来い！\N（貂）アア…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.99,0:17:34.03,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,仲間の死のつらさは\N軍師も兵士も変わんねえ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.09,0:17:34.15,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,The pain of losing comrades is no different for a strategist as it is for a soldier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.78,0:17:38.53,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,But we know the best way...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:38.53,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,だが そのつらさを\N乗り越える いちばんいい方法を
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.80,0:17:40.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,俺たちは知ってる
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.84,0:17:40.80,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,of overcoming that pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.72,0:18:02.05,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,We share it together, dilute it, then we fool around and blow it all away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.75,0:18:01.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）みんなで共有して 薄めて\Nバカ騒ぎして 吹っ飛ばすのさ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.83,0:18:07.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,お前も やれ！\Nもう飛信隊なんだからよ
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.89,0:18:05.45,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Why don't you join in?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.45,0:18:07.68,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You're part of the Feixin Unit now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.07,0:18:12.31,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Yes! You write it like this, like this, like this!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.90,0:18:14.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（笑い声）\N（兵士）ヒ～ッ！ 死ぬ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.31,0:18:14.19,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,Go to hell!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.19,0:18:15.87,Kingdom-Main,Guys,0,0,0,,The Guo Bei soldiers are the best!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.40,0:18:15.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）郭備兵 最高！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.81,0:18:17.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あれを 俺にやれと？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.87,0:18:18.32,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,You want me to do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.84,0:18:20.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）オッ！ 娘軍師 来た！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.86,0:18:21.11,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,It's the strategist girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.01,0:18:24.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）ギャーッ！ 見んといて！\N（兵士）ハハッ… 来た来た！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.11,0:18:23.59,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Ah, look!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.59,0:18:24.69,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,She's here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.65,0:18:27.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,こっち おいで 貂ちゃ～ん！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.69,0:18:27.49,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,C'mere, Miss Diao!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.49,0:18:28.95,Kingdom-Main,Pei,0,0,0,,I won't accept it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.52,0:18:30.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田永）俺は認めねえぞ\N（崇原）うるせえぞ 田永！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.95,0:18:30.21,Kingdom-Main,Cong,0,0,0,,Shup up, Tian Yong!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.30,0:18:34.33,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Xin...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.39,0:18:34.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信…\N（信）うん？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.03,0:18:37.99,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,な… 何だよ？
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.07,0:18:38.09,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wh-What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.48,0:18:41.02,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Let go of my hand already, it's embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.53,0:18:41.50,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,もう手ぇ離せよ　恥ずかしい\N（信）なっ…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.02,0:18:41.84,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Wha?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.76,0:18:44.37,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,てめえ この野郎！\N俺だって 別に…
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.84,0:18:44.39,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,You bastard! I wasn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.39,0:18:46.19,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Yeah, I know!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.47,0:18:46.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,分かってるよ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.57,0:18:53.31,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Okay, let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.64,0:18:53.41,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おし！ 行こうぜ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.85,0:18:56.71,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,おらぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:58.02,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Here comes Xin!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.81,0:18:59.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（兵士）信が来た！\N（兵士）お前(めえ)は来んな！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.02,0:18:59.63,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,You, stay outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.62,0:19:02.12,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（信）…んだと こら！\N（兵士）ウワッ！
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.63,0:19:01.17,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,What was that, asshole?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.42,0:19:04.62,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,Whadda ya mean stay outta here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.54,0:19:08.89,Kingdom-Thought,Diao,0,0,0,,Thank you, Xin... {Thought}
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.66,0:19:08.93,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（貂）ありがとうな 信
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.54,0:19:21.94,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,あっ… お～い！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.10,0:19:22.44,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:25.51,Kingdom-Main,Ping,0,0,0,,Vice Captain Chu Shui and the others are back!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.44,0:19:25.07,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楚水(そすい)副長たちの帰還だ！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.74,0:19:31.05,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,We brought Vice Captain Chu Shui.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.75,0:19:31.98,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田孝）楚水副長をお連れしました\N（貂）うん
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.05,0:19:32.11,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.44,0:19:37.48,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,With the headquarters moving on our own all over the place, getting supplies must've been pretty hard.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.48,0:19:37.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本陣が自分勝手に動き回るから\N補給作業はホントに大変だったね
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.85,0:19:41.39,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,これからは そういう仕事なんかも\N俺が受け持つから
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.89,0:19:41.44,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,I'll take on that sorta work from now on,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.44,0:19:43.99,Kingdom-Main,Diao,0,0,0,,so you can rest easy and go back to the front lines.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.49,0:19:43.96,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,安心して\N前線に復帰してもらっていいよ
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:51.87,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Who is this girl?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.40,0:19:51.87,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（楚水）誰ですか？ この小娘は
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.44,0:19:55.17,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,えっ？\N教えたって言ってませんでしたか？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.19,0:19:55.29,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Didn't you say you told him?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.86,0:19:57.45,Kingdom-Main,Chu,0,0,0,,Are you Lord Xin's little sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.87,0:19:58.57,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,信どのの妹か？\N（貂･田孝）いやいやいや！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.45,0:19:58.54,Kingdom-Main,Both,0,0,0,,No, no, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.11,0:20:02.08,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（田孝）彼女は河了貂といいまして\N我々の新しい軍師…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.21,0:20:02.92,Kingdom-Main-Alt,Tian,0,0,0,,{\a6}Her name is He Liao Diao and she's our new strategist. {Background}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.18,0:20:05.55,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,…っし！ やっと形が整ったな
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.31,0:20:05.49,Kingdom-Main,Xin,0,0,0,,All right. We're finally back in full form.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:04.65,Kingdom-Main-Alt,Dio,0,0,0,,{\a6}Yeah, yeah. Nice to meet you. {Background}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.65,0:20:05.80,Kingdom-Main-Alt,Chu,0,0,0,,{\a6}This girl...? {Background}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.75,0:20:12.20,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,From here, the Feixin Unit continued its steady momentum.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.78,0:20:12.42,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）ここから\N飛信隊は破竹の快進撃を続けた
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.46,0:20:16.09,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,うらぁ！
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.89,0:20:21.79,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,With the State of Wei focusing on Lijing as an opening to take back Shanyang,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.93,0:20:19.13,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（ﾅﾚｰﾀｰ）\N山陽奪還の突破口として―
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.43,0:20:23.90,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里井(りせい)の地に集結してきた魏国軍を\N逆に一網打尽にし
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:23.94,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,it instead turned out to be a big roundup of their forces.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.17,0:20:28.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,僅か10日ほどで\N里井を平定したのである
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.21,0:20:28.01,Kingdom-Main,Narr,0,0,0,,And in a mere 10 days Lijing was subjugated.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.65,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,The Feixin Unit is coming out here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.92,0:20:43.59,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（陸仙(りくせん)）飛信隊が こんな所まで…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.65,0:20:47.09,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,Yes. With no more enemies to defeat in Lijing,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.72,0:20:47.02,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,（蒙恬(もうてん)）ああ\N里井に討つ敵がいなくなったから
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:49.00,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,they're heading north.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:54.35,Kingdom - Titles Ep 36,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(150,204)}Shanyang {Left}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:54.35,Kingdom - Titles Ep 36,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(951,253)}Weizi {Middle}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.09,0:20:54.35,Kingdom - Titles Ep 36,,0,0,0,,{\fs60\pos(1058,555)}Lijing {Bottom}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.16,0:20:48.72,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,北上してきたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.09,0:20:52.63,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,楽華(がくか)隊と連携して\N微子(びし)の魏国軍を討とうって
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.10,0:20:54.03,Kingdom-Main,Sing,0,0,0,,A messenger told me they are joining up with the Yuehua Unit to take down the State of Wei army in Weizi.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.73,0:20:53.86,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,伝者が来たよ
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.20,0:20:59.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,どうやら ヤツら\N以前の力を取り戻したようですね
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.27,0:20:59.29,Kingdom-Main,Guy,0,0,0,,Well, it seems they've gotten the strength that they had before back.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.29,0:21:01.36,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,It's even more than before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.47,0:21:01.24,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,前以上さ\N（陸仙）えっ？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.84,0:21:03.83,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,In the battles where they captured Lijing,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.90,0:21:06.91,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里井の攻略戦…\N飛信隊は対峙(たいじ)した敵だけでなく―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.83,0:21:07.18,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,it wasn't just the enemies the Feixin Unit confronted that they beat.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.14,0:21:12.25,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里井の一帯にいた魏国軍全てを\N相手にしたような戦いを展開した
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.18,0:21:12.37,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,That battle developed into them fighting all of the State of Wei armies in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.01,0:21:17.36,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,At times, they made use of ally State of Qin Army positions and assistance
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.05,0:21:17.19,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,時には 味方の秦国(しんこく)軍の配置や\N支援を利用して
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.36,0:21:21.91,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,and saw all of Lijing as one large battlefield on which they were victorious.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.49,0:21:21.92,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,里井全体を１つの戦場と見立てて\Nそれに勝利した
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.94,0:21:27.18,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,In other words, they succeeded in a "wide scale battle".
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.99,0:21:27.10,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,つまり 広域戦をやってのけたんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.51,0:21:33.51,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,The Feixin Unit has clearly gained a power they did not have up till now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.63,0:21:33.20,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,飛信隊は明らかに 今まで\N持っていなかった力を手に入れた
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.56,0:21:38.77,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,And with the Feixin Unit currently being an independent reserve unit
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.67,0:21:38.77,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,独立遊軍としての形が\Nできつつある今の飛信隊は―
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.28,0:21:41.14,Default-ja,,0,0,0,,本当に強いぞ
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.33,0:21:41.46,Kingdom-Main,Tian,0,0,0,,they are truly strong.
